886
01:04:33,220 --> 01:04:35,350
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku tidak suka pria gampangan sepertimu.</i></font>

887
01:04:35,350 --> 01:04:36,550
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Memang ada yang kau sukai?</i></font>

888
01:04:36,550 --> 01:04:37,550
